{"tid":1807524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似支那人放天燈 火燒德國動物園 逾30隻動物被燒死","createTime":"2020-01-02T01:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T09:19:26.000Z","uid":34771,"like":423,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"38dfacb134fee85d3d64f672f95cd03f95c923a4","tid":1807524,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375256&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=219b1ff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375256&h=cf1c3b25\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375256</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】德國西部有動物園起火，超過三十隻動物燒死，警方指是有人放天燈引起。<br />\n<br />\n克雷菲爾德動物園的猿猴館燒通頂，消防員只能在裏面救出一隻40歲雌性黑猩猩及一隻年輕黑猩猩，而除了靈長目動物，燒死的還有果蝠及雀鳥等。火警在踏入元旦後不久發生，目擊者指見到有天燈飄起後，動物園便失火。<br />\n<br />\n調查員亦在現場找到用過但未完全燒毀的燈籠，已有人向警方投案，正被盤問。放天燈在德國屬違法行為，並不常見。"},{"pid":"9ec76793a416428290311360106d956c1105a1e3","tid":1807524,"uid":108696,"like":12,"dislike":45,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"真香"},{"pid":"8c92c74332c5be57ab488b68bf841362946206f8","tid":1807524,"uid":154054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:09:32.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"64c30b29c7f99c6c032ddd88da03ce4d7c6ce592","tid":1807524,"uid":144848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eb8119e755c85a9437e72d1d3d67d79c2fec29","tid":1807524,"uid":90392,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:10:07.000Z","msg":"啲無公德心嘅死垬蛆可唔可以冚家鏟?"},{"pid":"9ebc12b40cabde035a44c7da7e58d3808c8c0a4d","tid":1807524,"uid":154054,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-